{
  "description": "A dramatic, rocky cliff face is prominently featured, partially shrouded in mist. The cliff is composed of dark, jagged rock formations, layered and textured with weathering. Sparse vegetation, including small shrubs and vibrant green coniferous trees, clings to the rock face and its ledges.  The trees vary in height, with some towering near the summit. Above the cliff, mist and cloud cover create a sense of atmospheric depth, partially obscuring the higher peaks. Patches of snow are visible in crevices and higher elevations. The lighting suggests an overcast day, casting soft shadows and highlighting the textures of the rock and foliage.",
